Database reports are an excellent way to obtain

Database reports are an excellent way to obtain
state-of-the-art and current awareness information.
Each report provides abstracts of available reports on
a specific subject including: names/affiliations;
sources/retrieval information; extensive indexing; and
an abstract/summary of the project, program, results.
U.S. Patent Database reports are also included,
containing abstracts of issued U.S. patents.




