THE AIR FORCE OFFICE OF SCIENTIFIC RESEARCH

*  The Air Force Office of Scientific Research (AFOSR)
 ...has started a competition to support DoD's U.S.-Japan
Industry and Technology Management Training Program. The goal of
the program is to learn about Japanese industry and technology
methods for the creative use of science and technology in the
U.S. The deadline for submitting proposals is June 8. Contact Dr.
Koto White at 202/767-4969.



