*  The Department of Energy (DoE) ... is looking for
industry partners for the creation of a Solar Enterprise Zone
(SEZ) in Nevada. DoE aims to establish a joint private/government
partnership for the development of solar technologies. DoE hopes
to including options for local manufacturing, economic assistance
and infrastructure development. Call John Lewis at 303/275-4739.



